# Welcome to Backwards Development
This server is a haven for those who have an idea they would like to show people, for tools and applications to flourish.

## The Bots
This server has multiple bots who're here to help you with whatever you may need,
some play music, some moderate and some are simply here to make your visit more enjoyable.To see what the bots have to offer, run the help command followed by the bots name!
